==[[Catalan]]==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[portare]]''

===Verb===
'''portar'''
# to [[carry]]: Porta les maletes = He carries the suitcase
# to [[bring]]: Porta un entrepà per a tu! = Bring a sandwich with you! 
# to [[wear]]: Porto una samarreta blava = I wear a blue T-shirt

===Derived terms===
*[[emportar]]
*[[portejador]]

